  "text": "The efficacy of TMS in cortical modulation has been demonstrated in several studies: in a review of 51 experiments with an overall sample of 650 participants the authors reported robust effects of ~1 h duration on a cerebral physiologic index (EEG) after a single session of TMS [CITATION_1] .",
